PROTOCOL:
=========

  [number of subproblems]
  [SUBPROBLEM 1]
  .
  .
  .
  [SUBPROBLEM n]

SUBPROBLEM:
===========

  [number of segments]
  [segment 1 id] [segment 1 cost]
  .
  .
  .
  [segment n id] [segment n cost]
  [number of linear constraints]
  [LINEAR CONSTRAINT 1]
  .
  .
  .
  [LINEAR CONSTRAINT m]

LINEAR CONSTRAINT:
==================

  [value as float] ["<=" or "=="] [number of segments] [segment id 1] ... -[segment n] ... -[segment n+1] ... [segment id m]
